{"tid":2188545,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內蒙鎮壓反漢語教學示威 《洛杉磯時報》記者採訪遭勒頸驅逐離境","createTime":"2020-09-04T10:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T16:01:27.000Z","uid":240362,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fda44d4140f289170fd79deb17fb30ca7076f678","tid":2188545,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:01:19.000Z","msg":"內蒙古自治區本學年度開始推行所謂「雙語教學」，要將過去以蒙語為主的中小學教育逐漸改為以漢語為主，引發民眾普遍不滿，發起大規模示威遊行要求撤銷。但官員拒絕讓步，更將示威定性為「受境外勢力煽動」。與此同時，內蒙古巴彥淖爾公安局3日發佈了《關於依法嚴厲打擊涉國家統編教材使用違法犯罪行為的通告》（以下簡稱《通告》），指有「別有用心」人士歪曲國家政策，造謠傳謠，煽動、挑唆民眾非法集會、遊行，公安局將依法嚴厲打擊。美國《洛杉磯時報》3日報道，旗下有女記者於採訪期間遭當局拘留，事後更被驅逐出境，事件難免令人聯想到北京將蒙古反漢語的議題與香港扣在一起，才出現有美媒記者採訪期間被阻，甚至被驅逐離境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200904/BALCI33XX5GX7HYHO3JYMAZNQM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200904%2FBALCI33XX5GX7HYHO3JYMAZNQM%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cb7zmW0KSjJ%2FkJHMgTQKA%2BU%3D&h=bd95fb4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200904%2FBALCI33XX5GX7HYHO3JYMAZNQM%2F&h=b3c801b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200904/BALCI33XX5GX7HYHO3JYMAZNQM/</a>"},{"pid":"2581ca763cd3fc0f6b9391040b885f4d847a07ac","tid":2188545,"uid":231583,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:02:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b5e05eac0c88e8df87cd4185ad1ea005fa043fd","tid":2188545,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2581ca763cd3fc0f6b9391040b885f4d847a07ac","tid":2188545,"uid":231583,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:02:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\